            <div class="heading">
                <h2>We arrive in the evening.</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="paragraph">
                <p> The view from the airplane window seems familiar. For us, like millions of other travelers, Hamad International Airport has been a regular transfer point. 
                    Actually this Airport deserves an individual story not just a light touch. Maybe someday I will do it.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="imageBlog">
                <a href="/Qatar_part_I/Picture 005.jpeg"><img src="/Qatar_part_I/Picture 005.jpeg"></a>
                <a href="/Qatar_part_I/Picture 006.jpg"><img src="/Qatar_part_I/Picture 006.jpg"></a>
                <a href="/Qatar_part_I/Picture 007.jpg"><img src="/Qatar_part_I/Picture 007.jpg"></a>
            </div>
